parameters: \N<Red Cap Boy>Stop it... Why are you doing this...!?

\N<Boy>Ahaha, he says stop. If you really want us to stop, try
harder to make us.

\N<Boy>That's right, come on, fight back. If you do, I might even
forgive you. Right, Fubii?

\N<Fubii>Haha, exactly. If you're a man, don't just take it lying
down—show some courage. Then maybe I and these guys will
start respecting you?
\N<Red Cap Boy>But... I've never been in a fight before...

\N<Fubii>Oh, is that so? Then you'll always be someone who just gets
beaten up. You're okay with that, aren't you?
\N<Red Cap Boy>That's not...
\N<Rame>...What are you doing?
\N<Red Cap Boy>Ah... Please, help me... Help me!
1_ラメ01a
\N<Fubii>Tsk tsk, hiding behind a girl. Are you even a man?
\N<Red Cap Boy>Ah... Ah...

\N<Rame>...What are you doing here? Don't tell me you guys are
picking on this boy...

\N<Boy>Move it, Rame. This guy's new to town. That's why we're
'educating' him. If you get it, then don't interfere.

\N<Boy>That's right, come on. If you can beat us, we'll stop,
that's what we're saying.
\N<Fubii>Ahaha, they say that but... what will you do?

\N<Rame>Even if you say that, there are four of you. That's not
fair, it's not manly.
\N<Boy>Not manly? What are you talking about?

\N<Rame>Because it's true, ganging up on one person like this...
that's what cowards do.

\N<Boy>Shut up! What do you mean not manly! A woman like you has no
right to say that!
\N<Boy>Hey, don't hide behind that girl forever, come over here!
\N<Red Cap Boy>Ah...!?
\N<Rame>Wait a minute! You guys...!
A

\N<Luda Soldier>The way of fighting they teach here has changed quite a bit
before and after the Luda soldiers arrived.

\N<Luda Soldier>But that's only natural. There's no point in fighting if you
don't win, right? The adults in town lost to Luda because
they were weak, didn't they?
